Anthony DOVE
v.
Debra SPELLER. No. 511P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 3, 2005. David J. Fillippeli, Jr., Kinston, for Debra Speller.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 5th day of October 2004 by Plaintiff for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 3rd day of March 2005."
